review.comment: I was driving in Miami to see my family and I got a traffic ticket while on probation so my probation officer violated me later on I find out I have a warrant that I don’t believe I deserved, subsequently I contacted the Musca Attorneys office and immediately they starting working on the case and less then 3 days they were able to set me a hearing and have everything dismissed I got a high level of service at a reasonable price I’m glad that I called them very helpful and I’d like to thanks Attorney Rachel Kuhl for her patient and great work she’s amazing.
